info.description:
PHPRPC is a lightweight, secure, cross-domain, platform-independent,
language-independent, envirment-independent, complex object supported, reference
parameters supported, content redirecting supported, session supported,
service-oriented, high performance remote procedure call protocol.

This project is implements of PHPRPC client and server for Python.
